<paragraph blockId="5.[130,777,304,1028]" pageId="5" pageNumber="46">
<emphasis box="[155,539,304,328]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="46">Florulae Insularum Australium Prodromus</emphasis>
: 16, taxon 89 (1786). — 
<taxonomicName authority="(G. Forst.)" authorityName="Sw." authorityYear="1788" baseAuthorityName="G. Forst." box="[131,409,330,355]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Rubiaceae" genus="Cephaelis" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Plantae" order="Gentianales" pageId="5" pageNumber="46" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="speciosa">
<emphasis box="[131,294,330,354]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="46">Cephaelis speciosa</emphasis>
(G. Forst.)
</taxonomicName>
, Spreng., 
<emphasis box="[506,703,330,354]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="46">Systema vegetabilium</emphasis>
1: 749 (1824). — 
<taxonomicName authority="(G. Forst.) Drake, Illustrationes Florae Insularum Maris Pacifici" authorityName="Griseb." authorityYear="1866" baseAuthorityName="G. Forst." class="Magnoliopsida" family="Celastraceae" genus="Uragoga" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Plantae" order="Celastrales" pageId="5" pageNumber="46" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="speciosa">
<emphasis box="[247,402,358,381]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="46">Uragoga speciosa</emphasis>
(G. Forst.) Drake, 
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="46">Illustrationes Florae Insularum Maris Pacifici</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
15: 38 (1890). — 
<typeStatus box="[522,617,384,408]" pageId="5" pageNumber="46">Lectotype</typeStatus>
, here designated: Society Islands,Tahiti, without locality or date (fl. buds), 
<emphasis box="[655,773,410,434]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="46">G. Forster 57</emphasis>
(GOET[GOET012552]!). The sheet is annotated “57. 
<taxonomicName authority="Prodr." authorityName="Prodr." class="Magnoliopsida" family="Rubiaceae" genus="Psychotria" kingdom="Plantae" order="Gentianales" pageId="5" pageNumber="46" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="speciosa">Psychotria speciosa Prodr.</taxonomicName>
89” perhaps in handwriting of G. Forster; on a second blue label is written “Original Forster” with a det. slip by F. R. Fosberg “57. 
<taxonomicName authority="Forst." authorityName="Forst." box="[176,413,516,540]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Rubiaceae" genus="Psychotria" kingdom="Plantae" order="Gentianales" pageId="5" pageNumber="46" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="speciosa">Psychotria speciosa Forst.</taxonomicName>
f. in 1986”. Due to the poor condition of the 
<typeStatus box="[189,278,542,566]" pageId="5" pageNumber="46">lectotype</typeStatus>
, we also designate the following specimen as epitype.
</paragraph>
