<subSubSection pageId="5" pageNumber="46" type="distribution">
<paragraph blockId="5.[130,777,304,1028]" pageId="5" pageNumber="46">
DISTRIBUTION, HABITAT AND ECOLOGY. — 
<taxonomicName box="[565,738,717,741]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Rubiaceae" genus="Psychotria" kingdom="Plantae" order="Gentianales" pageId="5" pageNumber="46" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="speciosa">
<emphasis box="[565,738,717,741]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="46">Psychotria speciosa</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
occurs as isolated plants in mid-elevation forests at 
<quantity box="[614,741,744,769]" metricMagnitude="3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="1.1" metricValueMax="1.5" metricValueMin="0.7" pageId="5" pageNumber="46" unit="m" value="1100.0" valueMax="1500.0" valueMin="700.0">700-1500 m</quantity>
. Its ecology is poorly known, but collectors’ notes indicate it is rare in high valleys along streams associated with species of 
<taxonomicName authority="Sm." authorityName="Sm." box="[617,735,796,822]" class="Polypodiopsida" family="Cyatheaceae" genus="Cyathea" kingdom="Plantae" order="Cyatheales" pageId="5" pageNumber="46" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[617,691,796,820]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="46">Cyathea</emphasis>
Sm.
</taxonomicName>
and 
<taxonomicName authority="J. R. Forst. &amp; G. Forst. Many" authorityName="J. R. Forst. &amp; G. Forst. Many" box="[131,523,823,848]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Gesneriaceae" genus="Cyrtandra" kingdom="Plantae" order="Lamiales" pageId="5" pageNumber="46" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[131,227,823,847]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="46">Cyrtandra</emphasis>
J. R. Forst. &amp; G. Forst. Many
</taxonomicName>
of these areas are invaded by 
<taxonomicName authority="DC." box="[162,387,849,874]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Melastomataceae" genus="Miconia" kingdom="Plantae" order="Myrtales" pageId="5" pageNumber="46" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="calvescens">
<emphasis box="[162,336,849,873]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="46">Miconia calvescens</emphasis>
DC.
</taxonomicName>
</paragraph>
